@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_baodof(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.69)))
    v1 = (v1 + 0.28)
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.abs(v1 + 0.34) - (v0 + 0.81 / v2 + 0.31)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.58 / v2 + 0.29)))
    data[tid] = v0
